<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.7.2">
<l>pantār melviral nalvaḷait tōḷi pāvai pūmakaḷ taṉṉoṭu muṭaṉē</l>
<l>vantā yeṉmaṉat tēmaṉṉi niṉṟāy mālvaṇ ṇāmaḻai pōloḷi vaṇṇā</l>
<l>cantō kāpauḻi yātait  tiriyā cāma vētiya ṉēneṭu mālē</l>
<l>yantō niṉṉaṭi yaṉṟimaṟ ṟaṟiyē ṉaḻuntūr mēlticai niṉṟavam māṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You who appeared along with the lady of the flower, the girl,</l>
<l rend="indent">the one whose arms [bear] fine bangles [who has] fingers as soft as cotton,</l>
<l>You who stays fixed in my mind, dark hued [lord],</l>
<l rend="indent">you the hue of splendor like a cloud,</l>
<l>Oh, Chāndogya, Bhaviṣya, Taittirīya, expert in the Sāma Veda,</l>
<l>Tall Māl, ahh, besides your feet, I do not know any[thing] other,</l>
<l rend="indent">lord who stands at the west side of Aḻuntūr.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
